"2019-11-18T19:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ad4bc53b4df7092bd7da9ad6027e910addd42f","tid":1736602,"uid":235161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5b83c1fb6ea12b87fc2ece67f01b816ca61250","tid":1736602,"uid":310301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:34:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64f43d5bc9ccb9e8a3e9a256bccecda75efccdf3","tid":1736602,"uid":288753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:34:53.000Z","msg":"求下大家，唔好再睇唔到！！同意就幫我推呀！！<br />\n唔識整火魔？唔夠膽買電油，汽油？<br />\n今晚和理非出左去？係咪有好大無力感？？？？係咪覺得有種人數已經唔係能夠成為籌碼既感覺？<br />\n<br />\n請你地自己判斷未來既２個建議：<br />\n<br />\n１～唔再出黎。<br />\n<br />\n２～呢幾日去超市，買定打邊爐氣樽同通渠水。要出黎果陣帶埋黎支援！！！前面火魔建造好既火牆，當狗隻同車經過或貼近時就打開樽蓋，掟出去火牆既附近，爐氣樽同通渠水都有一定重量，醒目睇位，係可以掟到好遠。<br />\n<br />\n請記緊，唔一定要比火燒到，支野先會爆，接口撞地有火花都會爆！！<br />\n其他有電子編程人士，起我底。<br />\n<br />\n求下大家，５個月啦，唔好再黙黙站，之前一堆人唱歌，舉標語，叫口號，真係已經用唔著！！！<br />\n求下大家，唔好再比狗隻謀殺啦，求下大家！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"9fda2719327652b24936fb0f3e4918e816432a01","tid":1736602,"uid":76958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:38:39.000Z","msg":"救到人就好 我地咩都會試下做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9a87a1b95993cd54bdcd3e2df4cc82e882726d","tid":1736602,"uid":233665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:40:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔犧牲都犧牲左<br />\n謹記教訓！"},{"pid":"7f56772a361a1f9fe83c810ae56e3445253ca08f","tid":1736602,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21c7338d5e153a7d0b7f98cf0cded9ac6bcd194","tid":1736602,"uid":326543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:44:06.000Z","msg":"個教訓都幾甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉"},{"pid":"d2a141e1e41b3d673098ea550b1afc5814595cc5","tid":1736602,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:47:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n首先，學生們如果是無辜的，就不要自首，因為只有罪犯才會自首！<br />\n<br />\n現時尖東商業區街頭企咗好多黑警甴，等班外面班黑警甴散咗先走啦，佢地冇可能永遠企在那裡阻住人返工和開舖，學生們暫時留在理大校內最安全。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>學生可先在 圖書館、課室、飯堂等 溫書和休息，如果黑警甴真係夠膽漠視國際譴責攻入校園，上到法庭都大把抗辯理由話係無辜，告你地唔入的，總好過現在就貿貿然衝出去被狗拉。身處理大的校外人員萬一被捕時可辯解話昨天入去理大搵朋友但無辜被困。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"884177256bf05024f36e1bb3661c792e5b66313b","tid":1736602,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97d611b706741871f057e3c6c45da0f78772f52c","tid":1736602,"uid":178092,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:32:27.000Z","msg":"今次教訓好撚大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:48:06.000Z","msg":"你地繼續唔用腦打陣地啦，成班on9"},{"pid":"f97f5b5274abf542eb7d6e803d74cfe994107295","tid":1736602,"uid":171234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:57:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db11a51d3fedd600f79f2bd0db3dd5e645bc3ffb","tid":1736602,"uid":13318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:58:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c993877675fff4b79b9cc5a32b3ce4bbbd59edbc","tid":1736602,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:01:17.000Z","msg":"今日真係好慘烈，手足唔好自殺求求你地"},{"pid":"fa3194bf8c52b13002806fc1c6ed04afe7ea68f0","tid":1736602,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c993877675fff4b79b9cc5a32b3ce4bbbd59edbc","tid":1736602,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:01:17.000Z","msg":"今日真係好慘烈，手足唔好自殺求求你地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T00:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji